subject: Cheerleaders
Football
Wages and Salaries
Suits and Litigation (Civil)
lead_paragraph: For humiliations, and for hundreds of hours of work and practices, Alyssa and her fellow cheerleaders on the Buffalo Jills received not a penny of wages.
